description: Application for non-material amendment to planning permission reference PA/13/01276, dated 26/03/2014, comprising internal and external alterations to Building A, including amended layout of the ground floor commercial units, residential lobbies and residents' facilities; amended layout and mix of residential units on the upper floors; amended alignment and position of windows, balconies and cladding panels; amended layout and design of 18th and 19th floors, and; introduction of conservatory to terrace at 10th floor level.
